{"article_id":"oRA0aqFybntU59Wh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Alexandria , Virginia","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( CNN )","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Lobbyist and former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort learned on Thursday","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that he will serve almost four years in prison","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"-- far short of what had been expected and recommended --","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"for financial fraud convictions","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"obtained by special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"as he investigated Manafort 's alleged collusion with the Russian government in 2016 .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"The crimes ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"though serious among white-collar offenses ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"did not relate directly to Manafort 's work as Trump 's 2016 campaign chairman .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Reacting to Manafort 's sentencing ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"President Donald Trump tweeted Friday morning ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"taking the judge 's remarks slightly out of context ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that the judge in the Manafort case and Manafort 's defense lawyer `` stated loudly and for the world to hear","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that there was NO COLLUSION with Russia . ''","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"`` But the Witch Hunt Hoax continues , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"he added ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"referring to the special counsel investigation .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"`` As you now add these statements to House & Senate Intelligence & Senator","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"( Richard )","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Burr .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"So bad for our Country ! ''","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Manafort , 69 , had been facing up to 25 years in prison , a sentence","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that could have essentially kept him in jail for the rest of his life .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Even at just under four years , the sentence is the longest","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"given yet to any defendant in the Mueller probe .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"It nearly concludes a two-year downfall","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that began","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"when Manafort 's financial ties to Ukraine came under scrutiny","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"while he led Trump 's presidential campaign .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Since then , Manafort ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"previously known for his jet black hair , expensive suits and Republican connections ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"has turned gray","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and physically declined .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"`` The sentence was a lot less","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"than the out of control Angry Democrat prosecutors wanted , ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"the President 's lawyer Rudy Giuliani said in a statement Friday","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"provided to CNN ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"attacking the Mueller team .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"`` They should be ashamed of their horrendous treatment of Paul Manafort","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"who they pressured relentlessly","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"because , unlike Michael Cohen , he would n't lie for them . ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The federal judge","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"who sentenced him on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"noted","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Manafort had committed serious crimes","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and has suffered in jail .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"The amount of time","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"he received","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"was `` just , ''","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Judge T.S . Ellis said .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"However , the sentence fell decades below what the court 's own recommendation had been","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and what the prosecutors supported .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Prosecutors in court said","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"they hoped","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"the sentence would be `` substantial . ''","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Ellis said","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"he thought","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that 19- to 25-year recommendation was excessive .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"`` Life is making choices , Mr. Manafort ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"and living with the choices","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"you make , ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Ellis said","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"before he delivered Manafort 's sentence on Thursday at a Virginia courthouse .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"`` You made choices","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to engage in criminal conduct . ''","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Manafort was convicted last summer for defrauding banks and the government , and for failing to pay taxes on millions of dollars in income","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"he had earned from Ukrainian political consulting .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"He had long been a target of federal investigators and Mueller 's team","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"-- and was expected to be a star cooperator in Mueller 's probe","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"when he pleaded guilty last September","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"following a conviction at trial .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"That cooperation fell apart soon afterward , however ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and prosecutors moved Manafort toward learning his two sentences from separate judges .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"He 'll receive a sentence from the other federal judge next week , for the two crimes","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"he pleaded guilty to last year","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"-- witness tampering and conspiracy","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"related to years of illegal Ukrainian lobbying and money laundering --","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"which could stack on top of the time","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"he received Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Before he was sentenced Thursday evening ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Manafort spoke briefly in court about how prayer and faith helped him .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"He asked the judge `` to be compassionate . ''","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"`` The person","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that I have been described as in public","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"is not someone","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"I recognize , ''","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"said Manafort ,","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"who was wearing a green inmate uniform ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"to the judge .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"`` To say","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that I feel humiliated and ashamed would be a gross understatement , ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"He 's also felt pain","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"watching his family suffer ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Manafort did not explicitly express regret for his crimes in court on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"which the judge noted later .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Prosecutor Greg Andres told Ellis","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"that Manafort never gave meaningful help during his cooperation with the special counsel 's office ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"despite spending 50 hours in cooperation interviews .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"`` It was n't information","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"we did n't know , ''","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Andres said .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"`` The reason","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he met for 50 hours","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"was because he lied . ''","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"While the judge read the sentence ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"Manafort and his wife , Kathleen ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"who was watching in the packed courtroom gallery ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"barely reacted .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Throughout the three-hour hearing , Manafort had been stoic , seated in a wheelchair","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"because of gout in his legs ,","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"his eyes cast down ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"shoulders hunched","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"and hands in his lap .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"After the hearing ended ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Manafort 's eyes appeared bloodshot","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"as he was wheeled out of the room , back into custody .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Manafort has been held in solitary confinement for nine months for his own safety ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"after he violated his bail terms","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"by contacting possible witnesses in his case .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"He will receive credit for the nine months","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"he has been in jail ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"the judge said on Thursday .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"His defense attorneys have requested","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"that he serve his sentence at a prison camp for federal inmates in Cumberland , Maryland .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Manafort will also have to pay restitution of at least $ 6 million for taxes","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"he never paid .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"Depending on the government 's forfeiture proceeding ,","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"that amount could go as high as $ 25 million ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"Ellis said .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Manafort also must pay a fine of $ 50,000 ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"and he will serve three years of supervised release","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"following his prison time .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Manafort has already turned over several of his homes and apartments to the federal government .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"Yet he is still a rich man ,","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"and has millions left in home equity and investments ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"prosecutors noted Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Ellis said during Thursday 's hearing","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"that Manafort is not being sentenced for anything","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"related to interference in the 2016 election .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"`` He is not before the court for anything","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"having to do with colluding with the Russian government , ''","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"the judge said .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"But in many ways , the Manafort case","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"-- which reached back almost a decade","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"to track the movement of money from his Ukrainian political consulting work , through the time","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"he was broke and working for Trump in 2016 --","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"has shaped Mueller 's actions for almost two years .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Manafort 's was the first indictment","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"Mueller announced in late 2017","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"and his team used the criminal prosecution","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"to ratchet up pressure on him throughout 2018","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"as it sought his cooperation on matters central to the probe .","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"At one point ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"after securing Manafort 's longtime deputy Rick Gates as a witness against him ,","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"prosecutors split his case in two ,","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"putting the more clear-cut financial crimes indictment in the fast-moving Northern Virginia federal court .","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"Manafort 's conviction at trial was a major win for Mueller","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"-- the only official certification from an impartial group of citizens","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"that Mueller had uncovered major crime .","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"`` What you saw today is the same thing","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"that we said from day one , ''","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"Manafort 's defense attorney Kevin Downing told the press after Thursday 's sentencing hearing .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"`` There is absolutely no evidence","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"that Paul Manafort was involved in any collusion with any government official from Russia . ''","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff , a California Democrat","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"who 's leading the House Intelligence Committee investigation of Trump on Capitol Hill ,","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"called Downing 's statement `` a deliberate appeal for a pardon . ''","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"`` The statement by Paul Manafort 's lawyer after an already lenient sentence","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"-- repeating the President 's mantra of no collusion --","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"was no accident , ''","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"Schiff tweeted on Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"The eight crimes","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"for which Manafort was sentenced on Thursday","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"include five convictions of tax fraud from 2010 through 2014 ,","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"hiding his foreign bank accounts from federal authorities in 2012","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"and defrauding two banks for more than $ 4 million in loans","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"intended for real estate .","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"At his trial , one juror refused to join the other 11","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"to convict him on 10 additional foreign banking and bank fraud charges .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"Prosecutors later dropped those counts .","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"Manafort did not testify in his own defense at his trial ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"which revealed a life of excess , even among high-rolling Washington lobbyists .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"He had bought ostrich and python jackets and luxury cars ,","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"and had souped up his Hamptons mansion with elaborate flowerbeds , home renovations and karaoke sets","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"because of his secret Ukrainian stream of cash ,","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"witnesses testified .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"At trial , accountants , a bookkeeper and Gates pointed to Manafort as the financial fraud mastermind .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":381,"left":0,"right":380,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":380,"left":256,"right":379,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":1,"right":255,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":255,"left":211,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":199,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":196,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":2,"right":195,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":195,"left":192,"right":194,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":5,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":197,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":203,"right":209,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":11,"right":202,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":200,"right":201,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":205,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":16,"right":204,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":207,"right":22,"relation":"evaluation